title: Fashion Passion and Other Stories - Felicity Wishes
description:
Felicity Wishes has lots of adventures - and three fantastic friends to share them with! Whether she&#039;s organising a fairy fashion club, watching the ballet, creating an organic garden or getting her fairy mixture all wrong - Felicity is a fairy who knows how to enjoy herself!

&#039;Felicity is the friendliest, most glittery fairy&#039; -- Children&#039;s Bookseller Buyer&#039;s Guide.
